item.description:
Generates a 60-second short-form video script using a viral hook + content template.

Pre-requisites:
- Get a hook_id: SELECT id FROM viral_hooks LIMIT 1;
- Get a template_id: SELECT id FROM content_templates LIMIT 1;

On success: Returns a script_id. Verify with: SELECT * FROM content_scripts ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1;

Captures a new lead from the landing page, adds to Beehiiv, tags them, and sends the welcome email with the 5-Minute Daily System download.

On success: Subscriber is created in email_subscribers. Verify with:
  SELECT * FROM email_subscribers ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1;
  SELECT * FROM email_subscriber_tags WHERE subscriber_id = '<id>';

Processes an affiliate commission when a purchase is made via an affiliate link.

Pre-requisites:
- Affiliate must exist: SELECT id FROM affiliates LIMIT 1;
- Purchase must exist: SELECT id FROM purchases LIMIT 1;

On success: Creates commission, updates affiliate totals, sends notification email.
Verify: SELECT * FROM affiliate_commissions ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1;

Simulates a Stripe customer.subscription.created event to test the membership sync workflow.

On success: Creates/updates memberships row, updates profile.is_member, logs membership_events.
Verify: SELECT * FROM memberships ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1;

